<h4 style="color: #DAA520;">Closed Beta: Patch 26 (Feb 24, 2014)</h4><ul><li>No longer builds into Oppression or Inevitability.</li><li>Base Health reduced to 150, down from 175.</li><li>Base Power reduced to 20, down from 32.</li><li>Now has the Unique Passive - Soul Collector.</li><li>Unique Passive - Soul Collector: Killing a minion, creature or worker permanently grants 4 bonus Health and 0.5 bonus power. The bonuses stack up to 30 times.</li><li>Price reduced to 1130, down from 1270.</li><li>Builds into: Decay and Strife</li></ul>